{"tid":325253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲有偏頭痛","createTime":"2017-07-17T05:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T18:09:14.000Z","uid":118623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d5bf621ec2943d0f1250bdb1bad289eaee7661","tid":325253,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"好撚陰濕<br />\n個頭成日冇啦啦鬼鬼鼠鼠隔唔中痛一下<br />\n搞到個人炆炆地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe643bc8b28c64c7c872ece071b975cbf707bae","tid":325253,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ac01e2df6e87879d5ef71b99b97aea4258e09d","tid":325253,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe155ce9f332b51c0b76b439034af383c36e1b05","tid":325253,"uid":1717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"有啊 成日都想忍住唔食止痛藥<br />\n但有時真係會痛到暈暈地 唔食唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5caef6a14e4655d7dd03492ce40ed3e81903dd2f","tid":325253,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"試過用D按摩電貼電個太陽穴<br />\n又真係有舒緩作用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cdbcc8e100e74b8eaf0bc6b07a85e3e28e9af1a","tid":325253,"uid":80579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"10歲左右就開始痛 有時真係痛到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一星期一次<br />\n必理痛都無用 去咗睇腦科啲藥都無用 但沖熱水涼對我有用 舒緩少少<br />\n利申19歲仔 諗起都灰"},{"pid":"1d75d80a1c4d795b4c5421280e3da8335ca6ab82","tid":325253,"uid":53207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"我都成日痛忍住唔食藥<br />\n頂唔順就食兩粒必理痛"},{"pid":"44f1818055959b795a0c595d0b5d7e0d5f5a0792","tid":325253,"uid":26397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:54:59.000Z","msg":"痛左4年 已經唔敢再食止痛藥 <br />\n痛個陣要覆message會痛到電話都想飛爛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ae930d61f0a7e7a57706cb8df463d454f48875","tid":325253,"uid":77709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"我都頭痛左十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一星期痛一至兩次<br />\n通常都係右半邊頭<br />\n有時會好似跟住心跳既頻率咁痛<br />\n但好多時都係因為車既冷氣吹到就會發作<br />\n室內既冷氣幾凍都唔會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下天麻魚頭湯都冇乜用<br />\n只可以食必理痛<br />\n有冇巴打一樣 跪求偏方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 照過個腦又冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49b35c3c5c824675cb474d21243c43ca678a14a","tid":325253,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:33:59.000Z","msg":"諗起就恐怖，以前中學有一段時間經常性偏頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原本都冇乜野，但一痛就半邊身冇力，好似癱咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到我住左一個星期醫院，做左勁多治療都搵唔到個病因，又食勁撚多藥！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲都唔係最崩潰！！<br />\n最！崩！潰！係！！！一feel到黎料，起碼半個鐘，對眼係濛查查，極暈！！！！！係睇！唔！到！野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩依家冇再偏頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />神秘地消失"},{"pid":"9a83eb33960766f5fbb039ad2eeb635f88f47fcb","tid":325253,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起就恐怖，以前中學有一段時間經常性偏頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原本都冇乜野，但一痛就半邊身冇力，好似癱咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到我住左一個星期醫院，做左勁多治療都搵唔到個病因，又食勁撚多藥！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲都唔係最崩潰！！<br />\n最！崩！潰！係！！！一feel到黎料，起碼半個鐘，對眼係濛查查，極暈！！！！！係睇！唔！到！野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩依家冇再偏頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />神秘地消失</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要照埋MRI 同埋測腦電波都唔知個病因，呢下先好野！！！啲膠水扯甩曬我啲頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9e219392d40d1bffd97be664f662f0e8706472","tid":325253,"uid":30914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"痛緊睇到呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f11ae491219b588acb4e7050ebd6e4937e42220","tid":325253,"uid":18635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n一痛就食日本個種特強EVE<br />\n無既話就食3粒Panadol 500mg <br />\n但通常Panadol 係無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedd0862a9b7b92782d6d876e57d7cadf07dfd6f","tid":325253,"uid":36839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪偏頭痛<br />\n以前周不時都試過一邊頭痛到裂開咁<br />\n發作之前，通常都會眼黑，睇唔到野咁<br />\n頭痛個陣好似就裂開咁，手腳無力，又試過痛到嘔，食必理痛都無用"},{"pid":"1411ee0bd10f2885be5bc673d9f46a823f9b2ab8","tid":325253,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:53:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n一痛就食日本個種特強EVE<br />\n無既話就食3粒Panadol 500mg <br />\n但通常Panadol 係無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好傷肝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食ibuprofen啦"},{"pid":"7d39f9f343e559cb23164ed725da33abf0309fa3","tid":325253,"uid":11843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:09:14.000Z","msg":"細細個有， 痛到仆街<br />\n怕光 眼痛 後腦有2個位 閃下閃下痛<br />\n痛到會嘔<br />\n大過左就冇事"}]}